Automata
</p>

<p>
Political lefts are very romantic if we considered them from their dreamers characteristic. Their hope for a better future comes into synchronization with contemporary spirit when the ongoing everyday life of most people is lower in quality. It is the visual evident when a data set of unemployment has been complied into a graph with ongoing years on an x axis and unemployment number on a y. The graph has been a classic argument for the left to say that neoliberalism in this era can not help with the problem of surplus populations. Contemporary lefts try to point proletariants to a better future by the radical change in the source of income. 
</p>
